Notes: Midwest Conference Tournament Championship...SNC clinches automatic bid to
NCAA Division III Tournament, its 13th overall and fifth in the last seven
years...SNC's Brianna Byrne makes two free throws with 6.5 seconds remaining
and CC's Haley Grana's 3-point attempt from 30 feet drew iron at buzzer.
Game.Officials: Jodi Duffe,  Amanda Went,  John Mariani
